rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Liberalitas is so remote,
it's a pain to get to, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0002
rows.name:
But when Kurukuru delivers a
letter, everyone smiles, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0003
rows.name:
So even if the wait at the port is long,
it's okay, mo! And I can nap as much as I
want as long as I make my deliveries, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0101
rows.name:
Are you the Rex who's
been sending money, mo?

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0105
rows.name:
That's right. Are you
the one delivering it?

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0102
rows.name:
Kurukuru doesn't deliver the money, mo.
Among couriers, you're famous as the fine
young man who sends allowances, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0103
rows.name:
But Kurukuru is the one
who delivers Correl-san's
cooking to Avaritia, mo!

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0104
rows.name:
There's no direct route from
here, so it's not freshly
made... mo. I'm sorry, mo.

rows.label: tlk42300061_01_msg0106
rows.name:
It's a long way, so it can't be
helped. Don't worry about it.
